{"tid":110190,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"曾俊華：由高民望特首立法23條，市民較易接受","createTime":"2017-02-06T13:43:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-07T14:33:15.000Z","uid":58099,"like":3,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9952b2446482f042c4e2963cb5c6b1190a1b1c8d","tid":110190,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:43:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/06/213453_aac61608dc78bc94232e72c0151acd22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F06%2F213453_aac61608dc78bc94232e72c0151acd22.jpg&h=c94f4496&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行政長官參選人曾俊華會見傳媒高層時說被問到拉票進展時，他說有信心「入到閘」，日日數算票數，但現階段不會公開。他又說，很多人政綱也未看便表態支持參選人，他感到奇怪。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華透露，發起眾籌競選經費，市民反應是意料之外，很高興有這麼多市民支持，已有超過兩萬人支持，籌得超過400萬元。<br />\n<br />\n至於基本法23條立法，曾俊華認為是憲制責任，由高民望特首立法，市民亦較易接受。<br />\n<br />\n曾俊華說，23條立法及重啟政改，可以同步推行，視乎當時社會情況，市民很想有政改，中央亦有此意願，香港人是明智的，中央會作出準確判斷，他會如實向中央反映意見。"},{"pid":"a60769176421943dfb86df6a2398386450ce5ec2","tid":110190,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:48:46.000Z","msg":"。"},{"pid":"db957a205a40512c9923703e206e883630faab9e","tid":110190,"uid":4942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:49:06.000Z","msg":"接你老母呀"},{"pid":"d13d423a945e05222053f2a2a34019d80547d5de","tid":110190,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:52:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 奈何好多港豬唔知咩事"},{"pid":"157ad4330a850bf8c76b09eaf8aff9f102b6e729","tid":110190,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:54:37.000Z","msg":"曾俊華=糖衣毒藥"},{"pid":"f836dad2c0ff761aafa7c2f38f684a6a3de6ada4","tid":110190,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-06T13:58:36.000Z","msg":"呢個年代仲叫人信中央<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"805ca3ea3fbf7b1ae39